Bharat Petroleum Said to Seek Low-Sulfur Crude for November

-- B y   S h e r r y   S u
-- 
2011-09-07T10:52:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-07/bharat-petroleum-said-to-seek-low-sulfur-crude-for-november.html
Bharat Petroleum Corp.,  India ’s
second-largest state-run oil refiner, is seeking to buy low-
sulfur crude for loading in the first half of November,
according to tender documents obtained by Bloomberg News.  Last month, the company canceled a tender for first half of
October loading crudes because of high offers, said two traders
